<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Order mail</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body{
            font-family: "poppins",sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;

        }
        .container{
            max-width: 600px;
            height: 100vh;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #4f5ef1;
            box-shadow:  0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, .1);
            color: #ffffff;
        }
        .message{
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 18px;
            margin-top: 50px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .message-ms{
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 18px;
            margin-bottom: 50px;
            padding-top: 50px;

        }
        .message-ms > h1 {
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 25px;
            font-weight: 600;

        }
        .course-info{
            margin: auto;
            padding: 20px 0 px;
            width: 100%;
            background-color: #fff;
            border-radius: 10px;
            margin-bottom:20px ;
            color: #000;
            box-shadow: 2px 2px 2px 2px rgba(206, 197,197, 0);

        } 

        .course-name{
            font-size: 24px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .purchase-info{
            font-size: 16px;
        }
        .total{
            font-size: 18px;
            text-align: right;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
        .footer{
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 100px;
            color: #fff;

        }
        .footer > p > a{
text-decoration: none;
display: inline-block;
color: #fff;
        }
        .flex{
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: space-between;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #9999993f;
        }
        .flex  h4{
            font-weight: 400;
            margin-top: 5px;
        }
        .flex.lg{
            width:85%;
            margin: auto;
            border-bottom: none;
        }
        .first-ad{
            text-transform: uppercase;
            color: #0000006c;
            font-size: 16px;
            padding: 5px  0 px;
            width: 1px;
        }
        .first-td{
            font-weight: 600 !important;
        }
        .second-sd{
            font-size: 15px;
            color: #000000af;
            font-weight: 500 !important;
        }
         .title{
            font-size: 16px !important;
         }
        
         table{
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse:collapse ;
         }
         td{
            padding: 10px;
            text-align: center;
            width: 28.33%;
         }
         .td.col-2{
            width: 100%;
            text-align: left;
            padding:0px ;
            margin: 0;
         }
         .m-auto{
            width: 100%;
            margin: auto;
          }
          .table-row{
            width: 70%;
            display: block;
            margin: auto;
            padding: 10px 0;
          }


    </style>
</head>
<body>
   <div class="container">
    <div class="message-ms">
        <h1>Your Elerning  order  is confirmed</h1>
        <p>And  we are  just  as excited  as you  are </p>
    </div>
    <br><br>
    <div class="course-info">
        <h4> Here's  what  you ordered   </h4>
        <table style="border-bottom:1px  solid  #000000af ;">
            <tr>
                <td>
                    Order  #:  <=%  order. _id %>
                </td>
                <td>
                    Order Date: <%=  order.date %>
                </td>
                
            </tr>
        </table>
        <table style="width: 90%; margin: auto; display: flex;">
            <tr>
                <td class="first-td">Item</td>
                <td class="first-td">Qty</td>
                <td class="first td">cost</td>
            </tr>
        </table>
        <table style="width: 90%; margin: auto; display: flex;">
            <tr>
                <td class="second-sd"><%= order.name %></td>
                <td class="second-sd">1</td>
                <td class="second-sd"><%= order.price %></td>
            </tr>
        </table>

        <table class="table-row" style="margin-top:-20px ;">
            <tr>
                <td class="col-2">Total:</td>
                <td class="col-2"><=% order.price %><td>

            </tr>
        </table>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
        <p>
            If  you have  any questions ,pls  conteact  our support team at 
            <a href="mailto:ayushkumarnbd125@gamil.com">support@gamil.com</a>
        </p>
        <p>&copy : 2024  LMS . All  rights  reserved </p>
    </div>
   </div> 

</body>
</html>